#| msgid "Actions"
msgid "action"
msgstr "Azioni"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Action is a callable, class, or class method that handles a matched route and returns a response.  Read more in [\"Actions\"](structure/action.md)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "alias"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Alias is a string used by Yii to refer to the class or directory such as `@app/vendor`.  Read more in [\"Aliases\"](concept/aliases.md)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "Application structure"
msgid "application"
msgstr "Struttura applicativa"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Application is an object that starts up, handles a request through configured middleware, and shuts down.  Read more in [\"Application\"](structure/application.md)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "asset"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Asset refers to a resource file. Typically, it contains JavaScript or CSS code but can be any static content accessed via HTTP.  Read more in [\"Assets\"](views/asset.md)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "asset bundle"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Asset bundle is a PHP class that declares a group of CSS, JavaScript, image, or font files that should be published and registered together.  Read more in [\"Asset Bundles\"](views/asset.md#asset-bundles)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid "Documentation"
msgid "authentication"
msgstr "Documentazione"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Authentication is the process of determining the identity of the current user.  Read more in [\"Authentication\"](security/authentication.md)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "authorization"
msgstr "Generazione della documentazione API"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Authorization is the process of checking whether an authenticated or anonymous user is allowed to perform an action.  Read more in [\"Authorization\"](security/authorization.md)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "autoloading"
msgstr "[Configurazione](concept/configuration.md)"

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Autoloading is the process of loading PHP classes automatically when they are first used.  Read more in [\"Class autoloading\"](concept/autoloading.md)."
msgstr ""

