#, no-wrap
msgid "bootstrap"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/glossary.md
msgid "Bootstrap is application startup code that prepares services, configuration, and runtime state before request handling.  Read more in [\"Configuration\"](concept/configuration.md)."
msgstr ""

